channel.title: Problems With Moparscape3.1
channel.description:

and it will be invisible in my inventory

item.title: Problems With Moparscape3.1
item.dc:creator: @televator0 televator0
item.description:
@televator0 wrote:

ok, i suggest now to click start server and instead to go on the fourm advertisment, and look for a server that is suitable to your needs.

moparscape 3.1 is just a way to play on other servers and not to play on a non-existing one, its only there if no servers are online and your really bored.

i hope this helped you out a little =)

Your senior member, Tele
